SUMMARY:Global Build-a-thon Hack!
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nIn this livestream\, we officially 
 kick off the Global Buildathon Hack\, bringing builders from around the wo
 rld together to apply what they’ve learned throughout the series and tur
 n ideas into real\, working AI solutions.\n\nWe’ll walk through the hack
 athon theme\, structure\, timelines\, and judging criteria\, highlight the
  tools and resources available to participants\, and share what success lo
 oks like - from learning outcomes to real‑world impact.\n\n-------------
 ----------------------------------\n[The Java-Script AI Build-a-thon](http
 s://aka.ms/JSAIBuildathon)\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! Lea
 rn more [here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1628/?wt.m
 c_id=meetup_S-1628_webpage_reactor)
