SUMMARY:Model Mondays - What's New In Foundry IQ?
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nFoundry IQ is a unified knowledge l
 ayer powered by Azure AI Search\, allowing agents to query and retrieve da
 ta for context engineering.\n\nJoin **Farzad Sunavala** as he demonstrates
  how the unified knowledge layer enables agents to access and utilize ente
 rprise data effectively.\n\n***\n\n[Explore the repo](https://github.com/m
 icrosoft/model-mondays/blob/main/docs/model-mondays/2026-03-16-s03-e13.md)
 \n📢 [Join the conversation on Discord!](https://aka.ms/model-mondays/di
 scord)\n\n📌 This session is a part of the Model Mondays series. [Learn 
 more here!](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1485/?wt.mc_i
 d=meetup_S-1485_webpage_reactor)
